Title: Fermions, Wigs, and Attractors
Authors: L. G. C. Gentile and P. A. Grassi and A. Marrani and A. Mezzalira
Abstract: We compute the modifications to the attractor mechanism due to fermionic corrections. In N=2, D=4 supergravity, at the fourth order, we find a new contribution to the horizon values of the scalar fields of the vector multiplets.
